data.description: This spacious and beautiful Bradenton home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Here's your chance to own the perfect family home or starter home. With a large patio and a yard big enough for a pool, this home offers great outdoor living spaces. It is the perfect choice for a first time home buyer or a growing family, as it has been completely renovated and includes upgrades. With solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom backsplashes, and designer faucets, the kitchen has been completely renovated. As with the kitchen, the bathroom features new hardware, granite countertops, a custom vanity, and granite countertops in the shower. Among the other upgrades, you will find a NEW ROOF (2022), NEW IMPACT WINDOWS THROUGHOUT (2022), NEW GARAGE DOOR (2022), NEW HVAC (2022), NEW WATER HEATER (2022), new flooring throughout, new paint, new LED light fixtures, and MORE!
